"&kig; , Isubiranyuma Icyo ari cyo cyose Guhindura... Ubwoko in i Inyandiko . "
"Koresha i <guiicon> Isubiranyuma </guiicon> /<guiicon> Gu&subiramo </"
"guiicon> Utubuto ku i Umwanyabikoresho , Cyangwa i Amahinanzira . "

